{"tid":1764223,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"私家車粉嶺公路失控撼警車　兩男警受傷送院","createTime":"2019-12-01T03:05:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T13:31:57.000Z","uid":212626,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4875c54bb8e0ad6e19fe2b1fa17b8e0ed3efa13e","tid":1764223,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T03:05:50.000Z","msg":"上水發生交通意外。凌晨2時05分，一輛私家車疑因故障，停泊於粉嶺公路及掃管埔路往粉嶺公路支路間的影線，一輛警車駛至處理有關事故，並停泊於上址影線位置。其間一輛私家車沿粉嶺公路往元朗方向二線行駛，至粉嶺公路近彩園路時懷疑失控撞向石壆，私家車衝前撞向停泊的警車，其後再打轉撞向停於影線上的私家車。<br />\n<br />\n意外中，警車上兩名男警報稱頸痛，清醒被送往北區醫院治理。涉事28歲江姓私家車司機酒精測試結果有度數但沒有超標，警方仍在調查意外原因。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20191201/s00001/1575161528002/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191201%2Fs00001%2F1575161528002%2F&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0B%2FcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=04b3ab10\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191201%2Fs00001%2F1575161528002%2F&h=2f599077\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20191201/s00001/1575161528002/</a>"},{"pid":"711ab270838aa070854780d9612af1e6d92e2485","tid":1764223,"uid":21545,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T03:06:54.000Z","msg":"司機冇事啊嘛？私家車個嗰"},{"pid":"418ac2c673b51a6a41088246792c328f6ac86148","tid":1764223,"uid":90946,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T03:10:54.000Z","msg":"而家d警察真係唔捱得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n撞下都受傷咁弱雞<br />\n紙做架？"},{"pid":"13892f1d30061152ac0af8f8141f9959a55516e8","tid":1764223,"uid":299647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T03:12:28.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借黎宣傳下，推比文宣組睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［廣告界不是condom] 推2號開始黎明行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1764